DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, June 2\, from 4 - 8 PM at Whispering Vine Fourth St. for a Flights & Flatbread tasting featuring Silver Oak and Twomey.\nTasting Fee: $45 per person Includes the flight and one steak\, potato\, caramelized onion\, and lightly blue-cheesed flatbread. Limited to 50 guests.\nFeatured Wines:\n- Silver Oak Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon\n- Silver Oak Alexander Valley Cabernet Sauvignon\n- Twomey Sauvignon Blanc\n- Twomey Russian River Valley Pinot Noir\nFlight and flatbread included.
LOCATION:4201 W Fourth St Reno\, NV 89523
